arch sign
msg
Object TRAPDOOR.
Used like a PIT, this trap triggers
when something moves over it
and the weight of the object is higher
as the default value of the trapdoor.
When one time triggered, the trapdoor
stay permanent open.
The default weight of this trapdoor is
100000g = 100.0 kg
endmsg
x 3
y 7
end
