arch sign
msg
Different RUNES.
RUNES are not sys_objects like traps -
they are invisible and can be seen when
the player has "see_invisible". This will
make "see_invisible" more valuable.
Other spells like "detect magic" will
uncover the RUNE - they will lose
the invisible flag.
endmsg
x 3
y 9
end
